column2: SELECT TOP #  p.petroMag_u,p.petroMag_g,p.petroMag_r,p.petroMag_i,p.petroMag_z,p.petroMagErr_u,p.petroMagErr_g,p.petroMagErr_r,p.petroMagErr_i,p.petroMagErr_z,p.extinction_g,p.extinction_i,p.extinction_r,p.petroR5#_r,p.petroR9#_r,ISNULL(s.plate,#) as plate,ISNULL(s.mjd,#) as mjd,ISNULL(s.fiberid,#) as fiberid,ISNULL(s.z,#) as redshift,ISNULL(s.zErr,#) as redshiftErr,ISNULL(s.zWarning,#) as zWarning,ISNULL(s.class,#) as class  FROM ..PhotoObj AS p  LEFT OUTER JOIN ..SpecObj s ON p.objID = s.bestObjID  JOIN dbo.fGetObjFromRect(#,#,#,#) AS b ON p.objID = b.objID  WHERE p.petroMag_r > # AND p.petroMag_r < # AND ( p.type = #)
